  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.poster.avif?t=1764679179\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.webm?t=1764679179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.mp4?t=1764679179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid burnout or lack of concentration and let Laburantitos accompany you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This <strong>time management tool</strong> combines the functionality of the <strong>Pomodoro System</strong> with the customization of a <strong>Virtual Pet-style</strong> character.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/5222d3c97ca60a7e3ff2a3cab84756c4.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its goal is to assist workers and students in their daily work, <strong>taking breaks</strong> to relax and <strong>unwind</strong>, thus improving <strong>productivity</strong> and managing the day.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/8ad6b4961d1ce03c92ef1308eefef359.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create work-break <strong>cycles</strong>, choosing the <strong>number</strong> of cycles and the <strong>duration</strong> of each segment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the core loop, which avoids gamification and other constraints that keep you glued to the screen and prevent you from relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/086d2a0d82cd30ea17b52abb136313bd.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dress your Laburantito however you like! <strong>Choose their appearance</strong> and even the <strong>environment</strong> where they perform their tasks and take breaks.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.poster.avif?t=1764679179\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.webm?t=1764679179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/d03e15f3f6f5c281b6bb0995c9d06ce1.mp4?t=1764679179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid burnout or lack of concentration and let Laburantitos accompany you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This <strong>time management tool</strong> combines the functionality of the <strong>Pomodoro System</strong> with the customization of a <strong>Virtual Pet-style</strong> character.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/5222d3c97ca60a7e3ff2a3cab84756c4.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its goal is to assist workers and students in their daily work, <strong>taking breaks</strong> to relax and <strong>unwind</strong>, thus improving <strong>productivity</strong> and managing the day.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/8ad6b4961d1ce03c92ef1308eefef359.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create work-break <strong>cycles</strong>, choosing the <strong>number</strong> of cycles and the <strong>duration</strong> of each segment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the core loop, which avoids gamification and other constraints that keep you glued to the screen and prevent you from relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3683250/extras/086d2a0d82cd30ea17b52abb136313bd.avif?t=1764679179\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dress your Laburantito however you like! <strong>Choose their appearance</strong> and even the <strong>environment</strong> where they perform their tasks and take breaks.</p>",
